  "notes": "This is the first iteration of the Task Manager CLI project. It includes the necessary files and configurations to compile and run the application. The `TaskStore` class handles task operations, and the `cli.ts` file parses command-line arguments and interacts with the `TaskStore`. The Oracle tests should be used to verify that the implementation meets the requirements."
